description:
NoxPlayer (Nox App Player) 6.2.3.0
Nox App Player&#xA0;&#xA0;is an emulator of the mobile operating system, with which you can create an Android environment on your computer.


The interface emulator looks like the one that we are accustomed to seeing on our Android device, if you want, you can even switch to touch control.&#xA0;The main platform has a version of Android 4.4.2.&#xA0;If you want, you can not only download APK files from your computer, but you can work with the official store, downloading programs and games without problems, which of course is a big plus.


Nox App Player is perfect for testing games and programs, especially if you are a developer.&#xA0;The program will allow you to run several emulators on one computer at once.&#xA0;I wanted to note the possibility of connecting a gamepad or controller, and of course with the keyboard you can work.&#xA0;In general, I was pleased, sometimes I myself need an emulator, and I do not know which one to use, this one works without problems and glitches, as it behaves further, time will tell.

Developer&#xA0;: Nox Team&#xA0;
License&#xA0;: FreeWare&#xA0;
Language&#xA0;: English + Russian&#xA0;
Size&#xA0;: 315 MB&#xA0;
OS&#xA0;: Windows&#xA0;
Download&#xA0;:&#xA0;NoxPlayer (Nox App Player) 6.2.3.0
